HEADWORD: Gustatory
<hw>Gust"a*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
subservient to, the sense of taste; <as>as, the <ex>gustatory</ex> nerve
which supplies the front of the tongue</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
